             for 10s. at the Bird-in Hand at Cow-Cross, on Tuesday Morning; and that 
               <persName id="t17250224-60-person323">
                  John 
                  Coomes 
               <interp inst="t17250224-60-person323" type="surname" value="Coomes"></interp>
